        <div n="545-083Y" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Upon a maxim of Rochefoucault.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-1"> Wise <hi rend="underline">Rochefoucault</hi> a maxim writ,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-2"> Made up of <hi rend="underline">Malice, Truth</hi>, &amp; <hi rend="underline">wit</hi>:</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-3"> If what he says be not a <hi rend="underline">Joke</hi>,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-4"> We <hi rend="underline">Mortals</hi> are strange kind of <hi rend="underline">Folk</hi>.</l></lg><lg n="2" type="stanza"><l n="5" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-5">But hold──Before we further go,&#13;</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-6"> 'Tis fit the <hi rend="underline">Maxim</hi> we should know.</l></lg><lg n="3" type="triplet"><l n="7" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-7">He says “Whenever <hi rend="underline">Fortune</hi> sends</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-8"> “<hi rend="underline">Disasters</hi> to our <hi rend="underline">dearest Friends</hi>,</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-9"> “Although we <hi rend="underline">outwardly</hi> may grieve,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-10"> “We oft are <hi rend="underline">Laughing in our Sleve</hi>.</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-11"> And when I think upon't, this Minute,</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-12"> I fancy there is something in it.We see a <hi rend="underline">Comrade</hi> get a fall,</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-13" rend="indent(1)"> Yet <hi rend="underline">laugh</hi> our Hearts out, <hi rend="underline">one</hi> &amp; <hi rend="underline">all.Tom</hi> for a <hi rend="underline">wealthy Wife</hi> looks round</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-14"> A <hi rend="underline">Nymph</hi>, that brings <hi rend="underline">ten thousand</hi> pound,</l><l n="15" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-15"> He no where could have better pick·d;</l><l n="16" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-16"> A <hi rend="underline">Rival</hi> comes, &amp; <hi rend="underline">Tom</hi>────is nick'd──</l><l n="17" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-17"> See how behave his <hi rend="underline">Friends</hi> profest,</l><l n="18" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-18"> They turn the <hi rend="underline">Matter</hi> to a <hi rend="underline">Jest</hi>;</l><l n="19" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-19"> Loll out their Tongues, &amp; thus, they talk·d,<hi rend="underline">Poor </hi>Tom<hi rend="underline"> has got plaguy baulkd</hi>──!I could give Instances enough,</l><l n="20" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-20"> That <hi rend="underline">Human Friendship</hi> is but <hi rend="underline">Stuff</hi>.</l><l n="21" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-21"> Whene'er a <hi rend="underline">flatt'ring Puppy</hi> cries</l><l n="22" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-22"> You are his <hi rend="underline">Dearest Friend</hi>──; he <hi rend="underline">lyes</hi>:<gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/>Come, tell me truly woud you take well,</l><l n="23" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-23"> Suppose your <hi rend="underline">friend</hi> &amp; <hi rend="underline">you</hi> were <hi rend="underline">Equal</hi>,</l><l n="24" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-24"> To see him almost <hi rend="underline">foremost</hi> stand,</l><l n="25" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-25"> Affect to take the <hi rend="underline">upper Hand</hi>,</l><l n="26" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-26"> And strive to pass in <hi rend="underline">public</hi> View,</l><l n="27" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-27"> For much a <hi rend="underline">better Man</hi> than <hi rend="underline">you</hi>?</l><l n="28" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-28"> Envy I doubt, wou·d pow'rful prove,</l><l n="29" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-29"> And get the <hi rend="underline">better</hi> of your <hi rend="underline">Love</hi>;</l><l n="30" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-30"> 'Twoud please your Palate, like a feast,</l><l n="31" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-31"> To see him mortifyd at least────'Tis true, we talk of Friendship much,</l><l n="32" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-32"> But, who are they that can keep touch──?</l><l n="33" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-33"> True <hi rend="underline">Friendship</hi> in our Breasts requires</l><l n="34" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-34"> The same <hi rend="underline">Aversions</hi>, &amp; <hi rend="underline">Desires</hi>;</l><l n="35" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-35"> My <hi rend="underline">Freind</hi> Should have, when I complain,</l><l n="36" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-36"> A Fellow-feeling of my Pain.Yet, by Experience, oft we find,</l><l n="37" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-37"> Our <hi rend="underline">Friends</hi> are of a <hi rend="underline">diff'rent</hi> mind;</l><l n="38" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-38"> And, were I torturd with the Gout,</l><l n="39" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-39"> They·d <hi rend="underline">laugh</hi> to see me make a Rout,</l><l n="40" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-40"> Glad, that themselves coud Walk about.<gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/></l></lg><lg n="4" type="stanza"><l n="41" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-41">When you are <hi rend="underline">Sick</hi>, your <hi rend="underline">Friends</hi>, you say,</l><l n="42" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-42"> Will send their Howd'yes ev'ry Day:</l><l n="43" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-43"> Alas! that gives you small Relief────!</l><l n="44" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-44"> Thy send for <hi rend="underline">Manners</hi>──; not for <hi rend="underline">Grief</hi>──:</l><l n="45" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-45"> Nor, if you dyd, woud fail to go</l><l n="46" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-46"> That Ev'ning to a Puppet-shew────:</l><l n="47" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-47"> Yet come in time to <hi rend="underline">shew</hi> their <hi rend="underline">Loves</hi>,</l><l n="48" xml:id="spp-545-083Y-line-48"> And get a <hi rend="underline">Hatband, Scarf</hi>, &amp; <hi rend="underline">Gloves</hi>.<gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/>545-083Y   </l></lg></div>
